| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-0280 — Recovery Inhibition (qilin)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: b5190fc6-b279-56d4-bd0c-b1df2c8f31bb"
